title: Spirit - The Best of Spirit
description:
320K MP3 Files


No one took the late-60s East Coast sound further than (the aptly named) Randy California and his band mates in Spirit, who brought jazz, blues and classical into the psych-rock mix. Here&#039;s their 1973 best-of remastered plus five bonus cuts Silky Sam, Aren&#039;t You Glad, Im Truckin, So Little To Fly & Taurus. 16 tracks in all! Epic-legacy. 2003.
